# Reflection

## What I Learned

A high-quality research audit goes beyond checking whether statements are true. It also evaluates the strength of supporting evidence, the credibility of sources, the balance of different viewpoints, and whether conclusions logically follow from the available information.

---

## What I'd Do Differently

Cross-reference the AI-generated report with peer-reviewed research, industry reports, and systematic reviews to verify claims, identify unsupported conclusions, and strengthen the overall assessment.

